# Task Management API

тестовое задание для efficient mobile

## Tech Stack

- Laravel 12.53.0
- Inertia 2.3.17
- TailwindCSS 4.2.1
- React 19.2.4
- TypeScript 5.9.3
- Vite 7.3.1

## Requirements

- PHP 8.2 or higher
- Composer
- Node.js & NPM
- SQLite

